421
00:30:15,440 --> 00:30:17,919
I didn't come here to eat.
I have something to tell you.

422
00:30:18,119 --> 00:30:20,879
-Tell me then.
-Bi Qiu Qing. For me, you are...

423
00:30:21,039 --> 00:30:22,399
like my de Moivre...

