00:30:28,879 --> 00:30:31,879
-What is wrong with them?
-What did Li Ming Cheng say just now?

426
00:30:34,560 --> 00:30:36,600
Chairman. You have something to say?

427
00:30:36,999 --> 00:30:39,639
