493
00:33:56,440 --> 00:33:58,840
Li Ming Cheng, what do I lack?

494
00:33:59,239 --> 00:34:01,239
You can even dance with
Bi Qiu Jing, the nerd.

495
00:34:01,399 --> 00:34:04,080
Why can't you dance with me?
I don't care. You have to dance with me.

496
00:34:04,239 --> 00:34:06,519
I'm sorry.
I only dance with people I like.

497
00:34:06,840 --> 00:34:08,999
You. I don't care.
I want to dance with you.

498
00:34:09,120 --> 00:34:10,679
Come with me.

499
00:34:14,279 --> 00:34:15,759
What is this on your shirt?

500
00:34:17,840 --> 00:34:19,080
Let me take a look.

501
00:34:21,360 --> 00:34:23,400
The first line, Ohm's law.

502
00:34:23,560 --> 00:34:25,239
U/R=I.

503
00:34:25,439 --> 00:34:28,719
Second line, 1000mL=1L.
So, it's L.

504
00:34:28,880 --> 00:34:32,400
2/1O2 is O.

505
00:34:32,600 --> 00:34:35,560
The third line. Density=Mass/Volume

506
00:34:35,719 --> 00:34:37,039
m/ρ=V.

507
00:34:37,199 --> 00:34:39,039
The last one is
the equation of electric field.

508
00:34:39,160 --> 00:34:40,920
F/q=E.

509
00:34:41,120 --> 00:34:43,479
The third line is a linear function.

510
00:34:43,719 --> 00:34:46,239
